The '''Kre'fey family''' was a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] family to which several promimnent Bothan military officers belonged. It indirectly involved [[Borsk Fey'lya]], the [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], and three other Bothans that served in the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] and the [[Galactic Alliance Defense Force]]. They belonged to [[Clan Afey]].

